{"tid":243952,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[兩個政棍幾時死] 新東補選討論","createTime":"2017-05-15T04:47:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-17T16:32:18.000Z","uid":25334,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"85ddeedb467c811b6bc5ac019583b08ba1b785f3","tid":243952,"uid":25334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T04:47:50.000Z","msg":"梁游失去議席，本土派無力爭奪單議席單票制之補選。新東群魔亂舞，政棍蠢蠢欲動，當中以張秀賢及范國威聲勢最大。之前，張得馬鞍山之子麥潤培傾力支持，而范則獲劉細良邀請成為網台節目主持，兩個食人血饅頭嘅政棍爭奪補選席位，大戰一觸即發。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/u16apbj2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fu16apbj2&h=9d3c2d80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n張秀賢獲麥潤培支持證據<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/wtasxvqe\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fwtasxvqe&h=7f2cdd2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n范國威之政治關愛座言論<br />\n<br />\n母親節正日，張秀賢快閃影相，得到大量沙田區區議員支持，光譜遍及整個民主派。<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/734fc9rt\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F734fc9rt&h=ed4ed9c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/mik7fgnx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fmik7fgnx&h=6674b40c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/c9u8mifb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fc9u8mifb&h=07ed5bbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/h85yv3ad\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fh85yv3ad&h=af2c16da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/eg1tkn98\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Feg1tkn98&h=d5ef10f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/5fjenmth\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F5fjenmth&h=bd4786a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/a0rso4zc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fa0rso4zc&h=89216d22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n范國威都唔輸蝕，母親節正日於將軍澳派花，撰文支持HA，務求奪回本土派選票。<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/1dyxpwvj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F1dyxpwvj&h=3efd22d1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://holland.pk/opae0d2r\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fopae0d2r&h=3341b547&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌晒佢地老母啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，兩個政棍當初冇聲援過梁游，而家走去爭凳仔，食相好難睇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無論本民青幾垃圾，梁游被共產黨無理褫奪議席，本身就係不義。個位喺呢四年應該係屬於本民青，唔係嗰兩個政棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，本民青冇人選，唔代表嗰兩個政棍可以喺冇本民青endorsement下出選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0565333c86b0a08bca0eea3d6f062d17ea581543","tid":243952,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T05:16:32.000Z","msg":"射落海都唔比呢兩件垃圾"},{"pid":"2837c391637ea5ea1648cd025dc1abc9aa321528","tid":243952,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T05:53:16.000Z","msg":"冚家富又要出動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8de4f46ec302fa61ec793ebf6d9f64711522a5d7","tid":243952,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T06:57:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"92d128ae19778a8133d9d088f36ec742c92e46d8","tid":243952,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T07:37:09.000Z","msg":"政工作者"},{"pid":"5f0f63e237e4b793effbb9bc93e533d664366062","tid":243952,"uid":25334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T07:40:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冚家富又要出動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有張秀賢未必需要冚家富喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冚家副都係想范國威死姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74c468695618fa7d7c297ead2d0dde125fccded0","tid":243952,"uid":25334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T07:41:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔投本民青就係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n本民青出唔到人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個散一個潛，補選唔關佢哋事架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98fdb2416b906d0d45f9cd2c50a6daebc51449cc","tid":243952,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T07:50:12.000Z","msg":"因為佢地係泛民<br />\n本土派嘅議席佢地唔使問你"},{"pid":"ffc6a8101249636320ebb8e9ec7868b13e85197f","tid":243952,"uid":25334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T07:55:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為佢地係泛民<br />\n本土派嘅議席佢地唔使問你</blockquote><br />\n泛民內鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過好多泛民人都想范國威同新同盟收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56de5d2f61344b5ba5b8e60208702c69ada29167","tid":243952,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T07:59:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a256cb4a833f195832653adfd3c17df5b308d84f","tid":243952,"uid":27151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T11:41:08.000Z","msg":"麥潤培倒米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好記得當日條仆街點樣玩鳩陳國強<br />\n照舊有本土投本土, 冇本土投白票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},